Class DateRecognizerSinkFilter

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.lucene.analysis.TeeSinkTokenFilter.SinkFilter
      • org.apache.lucene.analysis.sinks.DateRecognizerSinkFilter 

  •        public class
       
        DateRecognizerSinkFilter
       
       extends
       
        TeeSinkTokenFilter.SinkFilter
    Attempts to parse the CharTermAttributeImpl.termBuffer() as a Date using a DateFormat . If the value is a Date, it will add it to the sink.
